[SN]TITLE[SN]
Man dies in Salford house fire

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A man has died in a house fire in Salford.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
The blaze broke out at a property in Berry Street, Clifton, just after midnight, police said.
The body of a man, who has not been named, was discovered inside the property by firefighters.
A joint investigation with Greater Manchester Fire and Rescue Service and Greater Manchester Police has been started to establish what caused the fire.
